Titolo: Pools of Darkness

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Pools of Darkness is a role-playing video game published by Strategic Simulations in 1991.  The cover art and introduction screen shows a female drow. It is the fourth (and final) entry in the Pool of Radiance series of Gold Box games, and the story is a continuation of the events after Secret of the Silver Blades. The novel loosely based on the game was released in 1992.  Like the previous games in the series, it is set in the Forgotten Realms, a campaign setting from Dungeons & Dragons.  Players must stop an invasion from an evil god, eventually traveling to other dimensions to confront his lieutenants.